de.esoco.lib.property

Interface Flags<F>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Flaggable<F>

    public interface Flags<F>
    An interface for objects that can have an arbitrary number of flags set on them. The flags can be of arbitrary types (typically strings or enums) and their existence can be queries with hasFlag(Object).
